    },
    {
      "span_id": "p060_s0013",
      "text": "4.2.16.1  Description",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        382.96,
        192.63,
        394.08
      ],
      "block_index": 9,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p060_s0014",
      "text": "The LINIT ELS requests the start of Loop Initialization on a designated loop.  The FL_Port connected",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        406.96,
        540.01,
        418.08
      ],
      "block_index": 10,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p060_s0015",
      "text": "to the loop addressed by the Loop Fabric Address shall originate a LIP of the type specified in the",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        418.96,
        539.92,
        430.08
      ],
      "block_index": 10,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p060_s0016",
      "text": "Payload and begin the Initialization Process as described in FC-AL-2. The LS_ACC Reply Sequence",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        430.96,
        539.95,
        442.08
      ],
      "block_index": 10,
      "line_index": 3,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p060_s0017",
      "text": "shall not be initiated before the FL_Port has transitioned from the OPEN-INIT to MONITORING",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        442.96,
        540.06,
        454.08
      ],
      "block_index": 10,
      "line_index": 4,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p060_s0018",
      "text": "State, and the Fabric Controller has completed sending any FAN ELS (see FC-AL-2).  If the LINIT",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        454.96,
        540.0,
        466.08
      ],
      "block_index": 10,
      "line_index": 5,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p060_s0019",
      "text": "ELS is received by a non-FL_Port, the port shall originate an LS_RJT with a reason code of \"Com-",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        466.96,
        540.02,
        478.08
      ],
      "block_index": 10,
      "line_index": 6,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p060_s0020",
      "text": "mand not supported\".",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        478.96,
        191.22,
        490.08
      ],
      "block_index": 10,
      "line_index": 7,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
